===Etymology===
''ad-'', from the Latin ''ad'', (to, toward) + [[''join'']]

===Intransitive Verb===
'''adjoin'''

# To be in [[contact]] with or [[close]] to
#: The [[park]] '''adjoins''' the [[lake]].

===Transitive Verb===
'''adjoin''' [[''adjoins'']]

# To be in contact or [[connection]] with
#:  The [[living room]] and [[dining room]] '''adjoin''' each other.

